  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1768667296\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1768667296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1768667296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lilly's Rescue is a 3d platformer set in an unknown and magical world, play it your way, improve your skills throughout the game and find your kitten and bring him home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/577be3e2d4219baf1f95ed128407f03d.poster.avif?t=1768667296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/577be3e2d4219baf1f95ed128407f03d.webm?t=1768667296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/577be3e2d4219baf1f95ed128407f03d.mp4?t=1768667296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>After entering television to save your kitten Lilly, you will have a brief journey through an unknown world full of magic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/88fd6ae037a1e08920d199e7e71154a9.poster.avif?t=1768667296\" width=668 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/88fd6ae037a1e08920d199e7e71154a9.webm?t=1768667296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/88fd6ae037a1e08920d199e7e71154a9.mp4?t=1768667296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1627420/extras/db1c9c1cfd67f7bf5a07cac9ab222457.webp?t=1768667296\" width=736 height=61 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Collect resources to improve your skills.<br></li><li> Cross the walls with your special ability<br></li><li> Rolling Stone Escape.<br></li><li> Mazes full of confusing exits.</li></ul>",
